          <p class= "faq-answer">
            Equity crowdfunding has recently become the most efficient way to raise money from people all over the world. There are two main types of crowdfunding: <u>Equity-based CrowdFunding</u>, in which investors receive equity ownership in the company, and <u>Rewards-Based CrowdFunding</u>, where individuals donate money to a project or company usually in exchange for perks, such as tickets or non-monetary rewards. DreamFunded is an equity crowdfunding platform, which enables investors to receive company equity in return for investment capital.</p><br>

