          <h2 class= "darkblue centered"> How Do I Make An Investment?</h2><br>

          <p class= "faq-answer">After registering and becoming a member, you will be able to browse the available investment opportunities in the “Investments” section of the DreamFunded website. For each investment opportunity, you will find a wealth of information about the company including; videos, presentations, analysis, deal terms, team profiles and more. You will also be able to comment, ask the issuer (company) questions, communicate with other investors. Once you identify a company you like and want to invest in, you will be able to sign all the relevant legal documents and invest securely using your bank account in minutes.</p>

